<h3 id="160">5.3. Activating POS visibility for POS users</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Now you define which functions and key figures are visible to <strong>Backend</strong> users in the plentymarkets App.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Activating rights for mobile access:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>Setup » Settings » User » Accounts</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Open a user account.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on the <strong>Mobile</strong> tab.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>In the <strong>Visible functions</strong> area, activate the option <strong>POS</strong>.</p>
