</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>Setup » Settings » User » Rights » User</strong>.<br>
→ The overview opens.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>*<em>Optional:</em>*In the filter settings on the left, enter an ID or a name to limit the search results.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Search</strong>.<br>
→ The user accounts that correspond to the search criteria are displayed.<br>
<em>Tip:</em>*Accounts that are greyed out have admin rights.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on the appropriate account.<br></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Resources</strong>.<br>
→ A list of available order referrers is displayed. In this list, each POS system linked to your plentymarkets system is shown as a separate order referrer.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Activate all POS systems on which the POS user should work.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> the settings.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<div class="admonitionblock warning">
