<p>For POS orders to be saved in plentymarkets correctly, every order must be associated with a contact. As such, you need to create an anonymous default user for casual customers. Proceed as described to create a default customer for POS orders. Only settings necessary to configure the default customer for POS orders are described. For general information about creating customers, refer to the <a href="/en/crm/managing-contacts">Managing contacts</a> page of the manual.</p>
