</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Printing a test page:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Open the plentymarkets app.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>plentymarkets App » Settings » POS</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Tap the menu symbol at the top right of the screen.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Tap <strong>Test print</strong>.<br>
→ The <strong>Test print</strong> window is displayed.</p>
</li>
